thread.title: Chris
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Chris

author: Chris
title: Chris
text: Pick up at airport on time even if a little hard to find (airport way finding issue). Friendly staff who are attentive to your needs but maybe not as timely as possible for those people waiting. Good no fuss examination of the vehicle at time of hand over to us and when we returned it. We did fill and clean ours after 3900 km and that helps considerably. While the car (Toyota Previa) was not new and we were not expecting new it ran without a hitch and was comfortable for 4 adults and all their gear.
